ur\u010dan \n | first = Vladim\u00edr \n | title = Ve\u013ekomoravsk\u00e9 hradisk\u00e1 \n | publisher = DAJAMA \n | location = Bratislava \n | year = 2013 \n | isbn = 978-80-8136-013-8 \n | language = Slovak \n | ref=harv\n}}\n*{{cite journal \n | last = Z\u00e1vodn\u00fd \n | first = Andrej\n | title = Distrib\u00facia sufixu -ava v slovenskej hydron\u00fdmii\n | trans-title = Distribution of the suffix -ava in the Slovak hydronymy \n | url=http://dspace.nbuv.gov.ua/bitstream/handle/123456789/39201/09-Zavodny-NEW.pdf?sequence=3\n | journal=Logos onomastiky\n | publisher=Donetsk National University\n | issue=2\n | year=2008\n | language = Slovak\n | access-date=13 July 2015\n | ref=harv\n}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.nitra.sk Nitra.sk] \u2013 Official Website\n* [http://www.nisys.sk/www/index.php?lang=en Official tourist guide of Nitra]\n\n{{Nitra District}}\n{{Slovak Seats}}\n{{commons category|Nitra}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Nitra| ]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Slovakia]]\n[[Category:Great Moravia]]\n", "name_user": "Sinaloa", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nitra"}
